stanza.line:
Glory to God in the highest! Glory to God! Glory to God!
Glory to God in the highest! Praise Him forever more.
Praise Him from whom all blessings flow;
Praise Him all creatures here below;
Praise Him above ye heav'nly hosts;
Praise Father, Son, and Holy Ghost.
Glory to God in the highest! Glory to God in the highest!
Glory! Glory! Glory! Glory! Glory to God in the highest!
